\c 43
\s Vanhu vanoenda Egipita vachitora naJeremiyawo
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jeremiya wakati apedza kuudza vanhu mashoko ose aJehovha Mwari wavo, aakange atumwa nawo kwavari naJehovha Mwari wavo, iwo mashoko awa ose,
\v 2 ipapo Azaria mwanakomana waHoshaia, naJohwanani mwanakomana waKarea, navarume vose, vaizvikudza, vakataura vachiti, kuna Jeremiya, Unoreva nhema, Jehovha Mwari wedu haana kukutuma kuzoti, Musaenda Egipita kundogarapo muri vatorwa;
\v 3 asi Bharuki mwanakomana waNeria ndiye unokumutsa pamusoro pedu, kuti tiiswe mumaoko avaKaradhea, kuti vatiuraye nokutitapira Bhabhironi.
\v 4 Naizvozvo Johwanani mwanakomana waKarea, navakuru vose vehondo, navanhu vose, havana kuteerera inzwi raJehovha, kuti vagare munyika yaJudha.
\v 5 Asi Johwanani mwanakomana waKarea, navakuru vose vehondo, vakatora vose vakasara vaJudha, vakange vadzoka kumarudzi ose kwavakadzingirwa, vachida kugara vari vatorwa munyika yaJudha,
\v 6 vaiti, varume navakadzi navana navakunda vamambo nomunhu upi noupi akange asiiwa naNebhuzaradhani mukuru wavarindi kuna Gedharia mwanakomana waAhikami, mwanakomana waShafani, pamwechete naJeremiya muporofita, naBharuki mwanakomana waNeria,
\v 7 vakandosvika kunyika yeEgipita; nekuti havana kuteerera inzwi raJehovha; vakandosvika Tapanesi.
\v 8 Ipapo shoko raJehovha rakasvika kuna Jeremiya paTapanesi, richiti,
\p
\v 9 Tora mabwe makuru muruoko rwako, uavige muvhu pakati pezvitina, pavanopinda napo paimba yaFarao paTapanesi, vanhu vose vaJudha vachizviona;
\v 10 ugoti kwavari, Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, mwari walsiraeri, Tarirai, ndichatuma shoko kundotora Nebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi, muranda wangu, ndiise chigaro chake choushe pamusoro pamabwe awa andakaviga; uchawarira pamusoro pawo jira rake rinobwinya.
\v 11 Uchauya achirova nyika yeEgipita; vakafanira rufu vachaiswa kurufu, vakafanira kutapwa vachaiswa kukutapwa, vakafanira munondo vachaiswa kumunondo.
\v 12 Ndichabatidza moto mudzimba dzavamwari veEgipita; uchadzipisa nokuvatapa; uchafuka nyika yeEgipita somufudzi unofuka nguwo yake, uchabvapo norugare.
\v 13 Uchaputsawo shongwe dzeBhetishemeshi, riri munyika yeEgipita; dzimba dzavamwari veEgipita uchadzipisa nomoto.
